author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Nepal and how the Internet their was rapidly censored overnight, people protested and even lost their lives just to stave off blatant censorship. We need to fight back and here is how. Thanks for watching!

title: People Are Dying Over Internet Censorship Now...
